ity to express yourself, a throat chakra bracelet could be the right choice for you. <br/><br/>If you simply want to create a balanced and healthy flow of energy between all seven chakras, a bracelet with a gemstone bead for each chakra could be the choice for you. <br/><br/>Another alternative is to use a bracelet stack – comprising a bracelet with a gemstone bead for each chakra, and one or two single-gem bracelets as a boost for a particularly blocked chakra. <br/><br/><br/><br/> <a class="defbut" href="/collections/chakra-collection">Shop Chakra Collection</a> <br/><br/><br/> </div></div>